          "title": "Lizard Brain - Unified Decision Engine",
          "content": "PURPOSE: Single LLM makes ALL autonomous decisions (no separate filter + selector)\n\nFLOW:\n1. Trigger Candidates - All triggers that passed their condition check\n2. Current Queue - Tasks already waiting to be executed\n3. System State - Metrics including memories, desires, user tasks, and persona goals\n4. Recent Activity - What ran recently (to avoid repetition)\n5. Unified LLM - ONE call decides what to execute next\n6. Task Execution - Chosen task is executed immediately\n7. Big Brother Reviewer - Periodic/error-based review via Claude Code\n\nKEY PRINCIPLE: One brain, one decision - task/goal aware, no queue bloat.\nSELF-HEALING: Big Brother reviews after errors or every 50 cycles.",
